com.pushtechnology.diffusion.transform.transformer

Class JSONTransformers

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pushtechnology.diffusion.transform.transformer.JSONTransformers

  • public final class JSONTransformers
extends Object
    Common Transformers for working with JSON.

    Many of the transformations are supported by Jackson. The behaviour of Jackson can be customised by providing modules when constructing the JSONTransformers that will be registered with the ObjectMapper.

    Author:
    Matt Champion 19/04/2017
